{"tid":987340,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"十年後，香港嘅母語仲會廣東話嗎？","createTime":"2019-01-19T08:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T09:28:33.000Z","uid":226231,"like":25,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"7d389afe236d8f5787b528cd65bc8ff5e508f6fc","tid":987340,"uid":226231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T08:42:15.000Z","msg":"當年輕的一代用普通話做母語，學校又唔再用廣東話授課<br />\n又越來越多香港人話要移民外國<br />\n每日又有150個大陸新移民入嚟香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n10後香港嘅母語仲會廣東話嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定係廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該係普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2722ceeb343a7745726cb5149d79f0ccbb0bda23","tid":987340,"uid":33004,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T08:43:47.000Z","msg":"十年後香港都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29cceb48eada7dfc105819d1c3e40e204f7efa7a","tid":987340,"uid":213441,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T08:44:16.000Z","msg":"好似話嚟緊有粒隕石會直剷北京 睇下林鄭食唔食到個勢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81103c3054dff0f113f89059589699875d08909","tid":987340,"uid":226231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2722ceeb343a7745726cb5149d79f0ccbb0bda23","tid":987340,"uid":33004,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T08:43:47.000Z","msg":"十年後香港都無埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T08:46:45.000Z","msg":"好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8d0ee2635b63742c279c5f40caa23e9d0e8ce4","tid":987340,"uid":226231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":